      <scopecontent id="aspace_fe68bcde3fc95e5509805565ac6cd49d">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection includes photographic negatives of Edward McKnight Kauffer's design work with Percy Lund, Humphries &amp; Co., for whom McKnight Kauffer served as art director in the 1930s.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
